319
00:28:00,790 --> 00:28:02,750
<i>or short-term memory loss.</i>

320
00:28:02,830 --> 00:28:04,840
<i>It's rare, but legit.</i>

321
00:28:06,590 --> 00:28:08,590
<i>But every time I see him...</i>

322
00:28:09,420 --> 00:28:11,340
