387
00:33:36,130 --> 00:33:38,540
- Kill him?
- Of course not!

388
00:33:38,630 --> 00:33:39,670
Hey.

389
00:33:39,750 --> 00:33:41,590
Sit down, okay? Sit.

390
00:33:42,420 --> 00:33:45,510
This has nothing to do with you.

391
00:33:45,590 --> 00:33:47,970
You helped me out, and I'm grateful.

392
00:33:48,930 --> 00:33:50,760
