01:25:07,970 --> 01:25:11,300
You don't remember where you've been
or what you've just done.

956
01:25:11,390 --> 01:25:15,010
No. I can't make new memories.
Everything just fades.

957
01:25:15,100 --> 01:25:17,810
- Then why did you come here?
- I found this in my pocket.

958
01:25:21,100 --> 01:25:22,600
<i>Your</i> pocket.

959
01:25:47,250 --> 01:25:50,380
Bar bet. Care to contribute?

960
01:25:50,470 --> 01:25:52,800
- No, thanks.
- It's for a lot of money.

961
01:25:53,390 --> 01:25:56,350
